textline.data: The system shall protect the passangers & crew from high cabin pressure.
The system shall store the pressure values for monitoring the cabin pressure curve.
The system shall alert the crew of high cabin pressure.
The system shall check if the cabin pressure exceeds a preset threshold.
The system shall raise alarm for a duration of 60 sec.
The system shall set a pressure threshold.
The system shall save the pressure values in a flash memory in a section entitled as
The system shall read the pressure value from a pressure sensor.
